{"tid":1611921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]「勇武」「和理非」唔係一個身份 防止落入階級對立陷阱","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:48:37.000Z","uid":103960,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a44d36bc6bfb8f62f9cb86f0247124490146dd7","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"係運動初期 我地好容易會將走得比較前嘅稱為「勇武」站得比較後嘅稱為「和理非」<br />\n呢個分法係香港抗爭悠久以來嘅一個叫法<br />\n<br />\n但除住運動越演越烈<br />\n呢兩個稱號慢慢演變成一個「身份」<br />\n甚至係「階級」 <br />\n咁樣就好容易落入對家<span style=\"color: orange;\">分化陷阱</span><br />\n結果雙方慢慢演變出階級鬥爭<br />\n<br />\n同時 係大搜捕時代 其實前線係越黎越需要更多人<br />\n兩個「身份」嘅標籤亦都會<strong>限制升級</strong><br />\n因為大家被<span style=\"color: orange;\">角色標籤</span>限制左自己嘅行動範圍<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野有必要大家考慮下點改進"},{"pid":"3d73bc124e2a365bd1ddae8bd5cefc458a63fc4d","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"060b726191f0524e9ef6f0f77efa97bd4698281f","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3161b38f575b0d990e2448419a1b02ce23ee0026","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"56d462d1196bf235ba6a806cac38241f416fdc13","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"要進化"},{"pid":"c534a399fb739ef1b2add857ce0ca2cdf535e19e","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56612fcade0191b70da433780188c7dac70a6721","tid":1611921,"uid":98993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9a37f7f3d65b893e364e587a9f3b288a7f18b18","tid":1611921,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-